  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to assess the effect of preoperatively administered intra venous
      magnesium sulfate in attenuating pressure response to laryngoscopy and endotracheal
      intubation in adult patients scheduled for elective non ocular surgery
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
